reviews.review_text:
best source I'm on nice headphones and DAC and this is the best sounding source i found in 2022. The M88 source is more open and very nice too, but I like the midrange bump on this source and it has a bit less audience noise. 

The Playing > Terrapin > Playing is worth the ride and the band is really listening well to eachother. a worthy precursor to the mighty Frost '82 shows
